public class AntPlusGeocachePcc.DeviceChangingCode
extends java.lang.Object

Defines the codes explaining the changes occurring to the device list received by the AntPlusGeocachePcc.IAvailableDeviceListReceiver.

Field Summary
static int ADDED_TO_LIST
          Indicates the specified device was added to the list.
static int NO_CHANGE
          Indicates the list hasn't changed since the last event.
static int PROGRAMMED
          Indicates the specified device was recently programmed and any existing data may have changed.
static int REMOVED_FROM_LIST
          Indicates the specified device was removed from the list.
